+			// References:
+			//   https://inbox.sourceware.org/cygwin/c98988a5-7e65-4282-b2a1-bb8e350d5fab@acm.org/T/
+			//   https://stackoverflow.com/questions/20959792/is-ssh-controlmaster-with-cygwin-on-windows-actually-possible
